00:05:08.490 --> 00:05:08.860
X.

00:05:08.890 --> 00:05:10.880
And that's where people are.

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:15.870
So, I think that is genuinely difficult to break away from

00:05:15.880 --> 00:05:15.880
.

