We want to get, have these ideas but not lose them

00:27:32.570 --> 00:27:32.880
.

00:27:33.030 --> 00:27:34.990
Not, like, lose that knowledge and, yeah, to

00:27:34.990 --> 00:27:39.480
be cultivating, cultivating knowledge and sharing it with whoever

00:27:39.480 --> 00:27:41.880
